<paragraph id="5860650FB580FF45FF23F7A92492FE4B" blockId="147.[151,1436,404,503]" pageId="147" pageNumber="148">
A monotypic genus (for identification see 
<bibRefCitation id="3C4E18FEB580FF45FDD8F7A9264CFE68" author="Garrison, R. W. &amp; von Ellenrieder, N. &amp; Louton, J. A." box="[620,846,441,468]" pageId="147" pageNumber="148" refId="ref191047" refString="Garrison, R. W., von Ellenrieder, N. &amp; Louton, J. A. (2006) The Dragonfly Genera (Odonata: Anisoptera of the New World. An Illustrated and Annotated Key. Johns Hopkins University Press, Baltimore, 368 pp." type="book" year="2006">
