<figureCitation id="C0E4798AB580FF45FB35F7A921D1FE6F" box="[1153,1235,440,467]" captionStart="FIGURE 85" captionStartId="147.[151,250,1959,1984]" captionTargetBox="[227,1361,993,1940]" captionTargetId="figure@147.[227,1361,993,1940]" captionTargetPageId="147" captionText="FIGURE 85. Argyrothemis argentea ♂, ECUADOR, Sucumbíos Province, Shushufindi, trails, small steams 3 km W of Shushufindi, 2+ km N off Hwy. 26 at km marker 17, 14 x 2009, photo J. T. Johnson." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3335791/files/figure.png" pageId="147" pageNumber="148">Fig. 85</figureCitation>
). Habitat is small, shaded forest streams.
</paragraph>
